<!-- Begin spacer right -->	<td rowspan="99"><img src="/design/knowledge/images/www-onepixel-trans.gif" border="0" width="7" height="1"/></td> <!-- End spacer -->
  

</tr>
</table>
<!-- ****************** End image ****************** -->

	</div><p>Mr Williams has learnt over the years that in our tropical environment the galvanised materials last no more than a couple of years because of the corrosion caused by the rapid vaporisation of the uric acid in the droppings of the birds. Therefore, he designed and constructed his own nest boxes from treated wood (Figure 6).</p> 
<div class="object-left">
<div class="clear"></div>


