<!-- ****************** End image ****************** -->

	</div><p>Broodiness is a management nightmare in every layer bird production; and Roslyn Farm is no exception. However, Mr Williams has designed an innovative system to break broodiness in his flock. The system involves isolation for about two weeks in a slatted-floor pen with supplementary light (Figure 7 a,b).</p> 
<div class="object-left">
<div class="clear"></div>


